{"tid":1552760,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"分化撚唔可怕，開始多分化撚代表既野先可怕","createTime":"2019-09-08T11:53:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T13:16:58.000Z","uid":205394,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9e09c982087a37641857b1904a2ccd6b5da54cc8","tid":1552760,"uid":205394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T11:53:34.000Z","msg":"核彈都唔割<br />\n呢個我地既口號<br />\n<br />\n但今日卻多左少少分化撚<br />\n原因無他<br />\n近期既撤回同埋美國既介入<br />\n開始令一部份人覺得勝利在即<br />\n所以想靜靜地贏左佢，見好就收<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n贏乜春呀？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">贏你老母呀</span><br />\n<br />\n咁多義士未救<br />\n黑警濫暴未追究<br />\n真普選未落實<br />\n831真相未查<br />\n<br />\n而家見好就收既話唔好話贏少少，係全敗<br />\n以後義士都唔會再企出黎，反正你地當人係condom<br />\n以後黑警乜都暴力解決，反正無人制止到佢地<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"f27cf631cc4aea6642b849bc43ebfc794e716081","tid":1552760,"uid":205394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T11:53:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb4ea7d3c992e5b89da63e4d593ca3cd672fc1ca","tid":1552760,"uid":205394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:16:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}